pageContext.claim: “There is collusion, but it's really with the Democrats and the Russians far more than it is with the Republicans and the Russians. So the witch hunt continues.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence of collusion between the Democrats and the Russians during the campaign. Trump makes the breathtaking claim that an FBI agent is guilty of "treason" when it is unclear exactly what he meant by the phrase "insurance policy" in a text message to his mistress.
